Here i'm tryting to make your better understanding about C++ programms
Using Terminal we will run programs
First of all open your terminal or
Use shortcut Ctrl+Alt+t
go to your work folder or directory like computation_physics
type file vi name with .cpp e.g vi enter_name.cpp then press enter.
click insert button then
paste following code
#include <iostream>
#include <string>
using namespace std;

int main() {
  string fullName;
  cout << "Type your full name: ";
  getline (cin, fullName);
  cout << "Your name is: " << fullName;
  return 0;
}
press Esc button
type :wq
Then g++ file name for example g++ enter_name.cpp press enter.
it will compile your C++ program.
Now we want to run program or take output following commands are used
